<font color="#FF0000">I AIN'T IGGNERUNT!</font><br>
<tt>Tue Jul 29  1:52:43 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Is it true that the harder you pull on the &quot;string&quot; the farther those big guns shoot?  I know that there were some big jerks on the lanyard when I was over there!  Anyway, how come &quot;Cannon Cocking, Redleg, Gunbunnies,&quot; are always trying to blow helicopter pilots out of the air.  I mean... just because we blew small sticks and a little bit of red dirt up their asses when we landed to give them their hot beer and spam...  No sense of humor!<br>
Comanches have no quarrel with Virginia boys (they smell like bacon and tobacco... two of my favorite perfumes.)  It was those pumpkin rolling, whiskey swilling, Tennessee hillbillies that came down here, destroyed our only permanent building in San Antonio, started pissing and moaning about having their knobby horses stolen.  Hell, my people had to move to Oklahoma and start eating Spam.<br>
And furthermore, no self respecting warrior eats fish... they come from beneath the water.  I will burn Cedar for this strange medicine man.<br><br>
P.S.  What is pineapple?  Pine trees have cones... not apples.  Wise Up! <br><br>
Mustang Two Four
